<h2>DVS Star Rating</h2>

<p>DVS star ratings for Euro IV, V and&nbsp;VI are now available from vehicle manufacturers. Contact your manufacturer&nbsp;to request a DVS star rating for your vehicle(s) or to enquire about the rating of a new vehicle. You will be asked to provide the chassis number for existing vehicle(s).</p>

<p>Your manufacturer will calculate the star rating of your vehicle(s) or a new vehicle based on the approved DVS Technical Protocol. They will tell you your&nbsp;DVS star rating and send a copy&nbsp;to TfL.</p>
